<view class="birthday-container"><view class="header"><image class="logo" src="/static/logo.png" mode="aspectFit"></image><text class="title">欢迎使用每日生活助手</text><text class="subtitle">请输入您的生日信息，我们将为您提供个性化的生活建议</text></view><view class="form-container"><view class="form-group"><text class="label">出生日期</text><picker class="picker" mode="date" value="{{birthday}}" data-event-opts="{{[['change',[['onBirthdayChange',['$event']]]]]}}" bindchange="__e"><view class="picker-value">{{birthday||'请选择日期'}}</view></picker></view><view class="form-group"><text class="label">出生时间</text><picker class="picker" mode="time" value="{{birthTime}}" data-event-opts="{{[['change',[['onBirthTimeChange',['$event']]]]]}}" bindchange="__e"><view class="picker-value">{{birthTime||'请选择时间'}}</view></picker></view><button class="submit-btn" disabled="{{!birthday||!birthTime}}" data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['saveBirthday',['$event']]]]]}}" bindtap="__e">开始使用</button><text class="tips">* 您的信息仅用于提供个性化的生活建议</text></view></view>